WEBVTT

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:31.840
otrov za muhe u kavu,

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:35.055
samljeti ga čašom

00:00:35.055 --> 00:00:36.944
i posuti mu ga po doručku.

00:00:38.044 --> 00:00:39.754
Kako ću olabaviti tepih

00:00:39.754 --> 00:00:42.142
na stepenicama 
da se spotakne i slomi vrat.

00:00:43.482 --> 00:00:45.109
Ali kad bi došao dan D, on bi

00:00:45.109 --> 00:00:47.361
svaki put preskočio tu stepenicu,

00:00:47.361 --> 00:00:49.190
izletio iz kuće

00:00:49.190 --> 00:00:51.030
bez gutljaja kave

00:00:51.030 --> 00:00:53.038
ili komadića doručka.

00:00:53.818 --> 00:00:55.104
Tolikih godina

00:00:55.104 --> 00:00:57.064
strahovao sam da će umrijeti

00:00:57.064 --> 00:00:59.138
prije no što ga stignem ubiti.

00:00:59.138 --> 00:01:03.730
(Smijeh)